00:09:57,034 --> 00:09:58,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Which team?</b></font>

159
00:09:58,544 --> 00:10:00,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's the "Hoshiya"Team.</b></font>

160
00:10:00,844 --> 00:10:05,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're looking for a young, premium racer.</b></font>

161
00:10:05,514 --> 00:10:09,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They want you to call them
right away to set up an interview.</b></font>

162
00:10:09,984 --> 00:10:14,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know for sure that you'll make a great pro!</b></font>

163
00:10:14,224 --> 00:10:16,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's very exciting.</b></font>

164
00:10:16,724 --> 00:10:19,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you gonna do?</b></font>

165
00:10:24,634 --> 00:10:26,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Turn it down for me.</b></font>

166
00:10:29,174 --> 00:10:34,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Like I said before,
I have no desire to go pro.</b></font>

167
00:10:34,144 --> 00:10:35,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What a waste!</b></font>

168
00:10:35,814 --> 00:10:39,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can't you at least talk to them?</b></font>

169
00:10:39,314 --> 00:10:41,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's right, Ryosuke.</b></font>

170
00:10:41,984 --> 00:10:45,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not interested in the
professional racing world.</b></font>

171
00:10:45,854 --> 00:10:49,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm only attracted to street racing,</b></font>

172
00:10:49,154 --> 00:10:52,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>where anyone can freely express himself.</b></font>

173
00:10:52,864 --> 00:10:58,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Gymkhana and circuit competitions</b></font>

174
00:10:58,164 --> 00:11:01,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>are the path I took to master street racing.</b></font>

175
00:11:01,704 --> 00:11:05,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right now, there's only one thing on my mind.</b></font>

176
00:11:05,544 --> 00:11:08,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six on Saturday.</b></font>

177
00:11:19,554 --> 00:11:21,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Done working?</b></font>

178
00:11:21,254 --> 00:11:23,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wanna go for a spin?</b></font>

179
00:11:23,454 --> 00:11:25,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--With you?
--Yeah.</b></font>

180
00:11:25,424 --> 00:11:29,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've readjusted the car, so I
thought I'd go for an easy drive.</b></font>

181
00:11:29,634 --> 00:11:31,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An easy drive?</b></font>

182
00:11:31,464 --> 00:11:34,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hate it when you talk like that.</b></font>

183
00:11:34,274 --> 00:11:37,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Akina Skate Center"</b></font>

184
00:11:41,314 --> 00:11:43,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Hey, Bunta?
--Yeah?</b></font>

185
00:11:43,644 --> 00:11:47,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Did you readjust the car for the big battle?</b></font>

186
00:11:47,784 --> 00:11:49,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right.</b></font>

187
00:11:49,484 --> 00:11:52,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think I'll speed up a little, Yuichi.</b></font>

188
00:11:56,424 --> 00:11:58,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hold on!</b></font>

189
00:11:59,464 --> 00:12:02,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm ready. Just a little bit, okay?</b></font>

190
00:12:24,014 --> 00:12:26,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Here comes the corner!</i></b></font>

191
00:12:33,194 --> 00:12:35,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What entry speed!</i></b></font>

192
00:12:35,134 --> 00:12:39,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I feel the G-force diagonally behind me.</i></b></font>

193
00:12:44,544 --> 00:12:47,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the heck are you doing?!</b></font>

194
00:12:47,474 --> 00:12:51,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I feel like having a smoke.</b></font>

195
00:12:51,384 --> 00:12:53,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Stop that!</b></font>

196
00:13:00,524 --> 00:13:02,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keep your eyes on the road!</b></font>

197
00:13:02,954 --> 00:13:04,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, no!</b></font>

198
00:13:08,634 --> 00:13:10,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not too bad.</b></font>

199
00:13:15,574 --> 00:13:18,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm serious this time!</b></font>

200
00:13:27,144 --> 00:13:29,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let me out!</b></font>

201
00:13:35,424 --> 00:13:40,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The tires and engine are adjusted for the race.</b></font>

202
00:13:40,194 --> 00:13:43,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How much horsepower does it have now?</b></font>

203
00:13:43,164 --> 00:13:48,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, I'd say its max is about 260 horsepower.</b></font>

204
00:13:48,104 --> 00:13:50,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>260 horsepower?!</b></font>

205
00:13:50,434 --> 00:13:52,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You downgraded it!</b></font>

206
00:13:52,844 --> 00:13:55,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It had at least 350 before.</b></font>

207
00:13:55,344 --> 00:13:57,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It did.</b></font>

208
00:13:57,374 --> 00:13:59,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Less horsepower?</b></font>

209
00:13:59,884 --> 00:14:03,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why did you have to make it slower?</b></font>

210
00:14:03,514 --> 00:14:05,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You should remember that, at times,</b></font>

211
00:14:05,684 --> 00:14:09,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you need less horsepower to run faster.</b></font>

212
00:14:09,294 --> 00:14:12,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's how deep street racing is.</b></font>

213
00:14:12,764 --> 00:14:17,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The key to downhill success
isn't power... it's balance.</b></font>

214
00:14:17,094 --> 00:14:19,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought I had adjusted my FC</b></font>

215
00:14:19,604 --> 00:14:24,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to make it as fast as possible
both uphill and downhill.</b></font>

216
00:14:24,474 --> 00:14:27,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I knew I could handle
even more power downhill,</b></font>

217
00:14:27,814 --> 00:14:31,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so I upgraded the turbine
and raised the firing speed.</b></font>

218
00:14:31,244 --> 00:14:35,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But in the end, I had to lose all that power.</b></font>

219
00:14:35,784 --> 00:14:38,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Regardless of the reason,</b></font>

220
00:14:38,454 --> 00:14:40,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>this downgrade was humiliating to me.</b></font>

221
00:14:40,554 --> 00:14:43,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I had to throw away my pride for this race.</b></font>

222
00:14:43,554 --> 00:14:48,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six is that tough of an opponent?</b></font>

223
00:14:48,434 --> 00:14:52,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm lucky that I've met
such an extraordinary racer.</b></font>

224
00:14:52,334 --> 00:14:56,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My racer blood is boiling up.</b></font>

225
00:14:56,074 --> 00:14:57,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's go.</b></font>

226
00:15:13,624 --> 00:15:16,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Less power, but fast!</i></b></font>

227
00:15:16,594 --> 00:15:19,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He clears the corners faster.</i></b></font>

228
00:15:19,994 --> 00:15:23,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There's no way my brother will lose to him now!</i></b></font>

229
00:15:26,464 --> 00:15:30,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Right now, I'm not Ryosuke</i>
<i>Takahashi of the Red Suns.</i></b></font>

230
00:15:30,804 --> 00:15:33,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm the lone wolf known as...</i></b></font>

231
00:15:33,004 --> 00:15:37,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...Akagi's White Comet.</i></b></font>

232
00:15:37,444 --> 00:15:41,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll win this battle, no matter what!</i></b></font>

233
00:15:49,454 --> 00:15:51,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

234
00:15:51,194 --> 00:15:52,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey!</b></font>

235
00:15:52,724 --> 00:15:56,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Race day is finally here!
--Yeah.</b></font>

236
00:15:56,834 --> 00:15:59,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It makes me angry, Takumi.</b></font>

237
00:15:59,334 --> 00:16:03,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Everyone thinks Ryosuke Takahashi will win.</b></font>

238
00:16:03,334 --> 00:16:08,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They say it's like a novice
fighting a heavyweight.</b></font>

239
00:16:08,144 --> 00:16:09,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Aren't you offended?</b></font>

240
00:16:09,974 --> 00:16:13,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Any plan for a big upset?</b></font>

241
00:16:13,044 --> 00:16:15,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let me see...</b></font>

242
00:16:17,754 --> 00:16:19,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No.</b></font>

243
00:16:32,264 --> 00:16:36,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Those racers are headed to the pass.</i></b></font>

244
00:16:36,274 --> 00:16:38,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's finally here.</i></b></font>

245
00:16:38,104 --> 00:16:39,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Boss?
--Yeah?</b></font>

246
00:16:39,844 --> 00:16:42,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've cleaned up outside.</b></font>

247
00:16:42,114 --> 00:16:43,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll see you tomorrow.</b></font>

248
00:16:43,444 --> 00:16:44,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Good job.</b></font>

249
00:16:44,944 --> 00:16:48,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--You're going to the race, right?
--Yes.</b></font>

250
00:16:48,184 --> 00:16:52,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You still don't think Takumi can win?</b></font>

251
00:16:52,024 --> 00:16:58,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No. I know he's exceptional,
but he's still in high school.</b></font>

252
00:16:58,064 --> 00:17:00,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He still has very little experience.</b></font>

253
00:17:00,964 --> 00:17:05,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder how long he'll even
be able to stay in the race.</b></font>

254
00:17:05,604 --> 00:17:08,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not me.</b></font>

255
00:17:08,104 --> 00:17:11,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I actually think he has a chance.</b></font>

256
00:17:11,374 --> 00:17:14,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Why?
--Because...</b></font>

257
00:17:21,284 --> 00:17:22,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Hey.
--Hey.</b></font>

258
00:17:22,914 --> 00:17:25,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I better hurry. Good night.</b></font>

259
00:17:25,284 --> 00:17:26,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

260
00:17:34,934 --> 00:17:39,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The only reason I think Takumi has a chance...</i></b></font>

261
00:17:39,434 --> 00:17:43,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...is that he's Bunta's son.</i></b></font>

262
00:17:43,234 --> 00:17:46,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The son of that crazy Bunta...</i></b></font>

263
00:17:55,014 --> 00:17:58,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The crowd is gigantic, as expected.</b></font>

264
00:17:58,354 --> 00:18:01,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If I were Takumi, I would want to run away.</b></font>

265
00:18:01,694 --> 00:18:05,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I would be petrified in
front of all these people.</b></font>

266
00:18:16,004 --> 00:18:19,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Isn't that Usui's Sileighty?
--Really?</b></font>

267
00:18:24,984 --> 00:18:26,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was right.</b></font>

268
00:18:26,144 --> 00:18:29,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--They're both cute.
--Yeah.</b></font>

269
00:18:29,784 --> 00:18:32,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How about around here?</b></font>

270
00:18:32,454 --> 00:18:35,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We may see some good tactics
at these complex corners.</b></font>

271
00:18:35,694 --> 00:18:37,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>By the way, Mako...</b></font>

272
00:18:37,454 --> 00:18:41,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...which one are you rooting for?</b></font>

273
00:18:42,794 --> 00:18:45,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Which one?</b></font>

274
00:18:45,464 --> 00:18:47,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six, right?</b></font>

275
00:18:47,464 --> 00:18:50,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Me, too.</b></font>

276
00:18:50,474 --> 00:18:53,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He has a mysterious charisma</b></font>

277
00:18:53,374 --> 00:18:56,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that only those who have
raced him can recognize.</b></font>

278
00:18:56,844 --> 00:19:00,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You want to root for him
even though he beat you.</b></font>

279
00:19:00,344 --> 00:19:02,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Besides, he's...</b></font>

280
00:19:02,854 --> 00:19:05,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...so cute! Right?</b></font>

281
00:19:05,484 --> 00:19:08,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come on, Sayuki.</b></font>

282
00:19:11,764 --> 00:19:13,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's almost 9:30.</b></font>

283
00:19:13,764 --> 00:19:15,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is it!</b></font>

284
00:19:15,664 --> 00:19:18,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm so pumped up!</b></font>

285
00:19:31,244 --> 00:19:34,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here come the Red Suns.</b></font>

286
00:19:40,254 --> 00:19:43,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Takahashi brothers are so cool!</b></font>

287
00:19:45,694 --> 00:19:49,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--This is the enemy, eh?
--Ryosuke!</b></font>

288
00:19:53,764 --> 00:19:56,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke Takahashi is finally here.</b></font>

289
00:19:56,404 --> 00:19:59,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now we wait for Takumi to show up.</b></font>

290
00:20:17,894 --> 00:20:20,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six is not here yet.</b></font>

291
00:20:20,324 --> 00:20:21,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I expected that.</b></font>

292
00:20:21,894 --> 00:20:25,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He always shows up at the very last minute.</b></font>

293
00:20:37,984 --> 00:20:39,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke...</b></font>

294
00:20:39,144 --> 00:20:43,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've been thinking about this for a long time,</b></font>

295
00:20:43,014 --> 00:20:45,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but when I lose a street race...</b></font>

296
00:20:45,924 --> 00:20:47,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...I'll retire.</b></font>

297
00:20:47,684 --> 00:20:50,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! What are you saying?</b></font>

298
00:20:50,194 --> 00:20:52,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'll never lose.</b></font>

299
00:20:52,764 --> 00:20:54,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just hear me out.</b></font>

300
00:20:54,764 --> 00:20:58,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>By "retire," I don't mean quitting racing.</b></font>

301
00:20:58,204 --> 00:21:00,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll just step down from the number-one spot.</b></font>

302
00:21:00,634 --> 00:21:04,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll still continue to contribute to the team.</b></font>

303
00:21:04,604 --> 00:21:08,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What about our "fastest in Kanto" plan?</b></font>

304
00:21:08,374 --> 00:21:11,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It can't happen without you!</b></font>

305
00:21:11,514 --> 00:21:13,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't make a face.</b></font>

306
00:21:13,844 --> 00:21:18,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have no intention of losing yet.</b></font>

307
00:21:18,024 --> 00:21:20,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Remember this, though...</b></font>

308
00:21:20,624 --> 00:21:26,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It is inevitable that someday
I will lose to someone.</b></font>

309
00:21:26,124 --> 00:21:30,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>By the way, there are only two racers</b></font>

310
00:21:30,034 --> 00:21:34,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>who I think could beat me one day.</b></font>

311
00:21:34,304 --> 00:21:37,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One of them is you, Keisuke.</b></font>

312
00:21:37,874 --> 00:21:40,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Me?
--That's right.</b></font>

313
00:21:40,474 --> 00:21:44,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see a racing genius within you.</b></font>

314
00:21:44,344 --> 00:21:47,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'll be even faster one day.</b></font>

315
00:21:47,684 --> 00:21:50,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And the other is...</b></font>

316
00:22:01,494 --> 00:22:04,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi is here!</b></font>

317
00:22:04,434 --> 00:22:07,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yay, Takumi!</b></font>

318
00:22:09,604 --> 00:22:15,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The other one is the Eight-Six, isn't it?</b></font>

319
00:22:15,044 --> 00:22:18,214
