333
00:24:08,454 --> 00:24:13,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Utsukushiku karen ni sake...</i></b></font>

334
00:24:13,694 --> 00:24:20,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kiseki no hana yo</i></b></font>

335
00:24:26,174 --> 00:24:27,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What's wrong, Takumi?</i></b></font>

336
00:24:27,904 --> 00:24:32,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've been taking challenges as they come,</i></b></font>

337
00:24:32,344 --> 00:24:36,154
